<!--
  Voice widget — recording ("equalizer · 2 bars" on pose).
  Two apricot bars per the design's 2-bar equalizer spec:
    - bar width: 10% of tile
    - bar centers: ±8.5% from tile center
    - corner radius: 6% of tile (capped at half-width => pill ends)
  Heights pick a representative non-rest frame (left tall, right short) so
  the static drawable still reads as "equalizer" rather than two equal pills.
-->
